  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two identical blocks labeled A and B.&nbsp; Block B is positioned to the left of block A and the blocks are connected by a horizontal rope labeled T. Block A is pulled horizontally to the right at a force labeled “F sub 0.” The blocks move horizontally to the right across a rough surface. The rough surface ends after point P, which is indicated to the right of block A.\" height=\"55\" src=\"/images/ff90b06de127f1dd177ddb4457f97505.png\" width=\"350\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two identical blocks <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>A</mtext></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>B</mtext></math></span></span> are connected by a lightweight rope. Block <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>A</mtext></math></span></span> is pulled to the right by a constant force <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"F sub 0\"><math alttext=\"F sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>F</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>. The blocks are moving to the right across a rough surface and approach point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>P</mtext></math></span></span>, where the rough surface transitions to a surface with negligible friction. How does the tension, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"T\"><math alttext=\"T\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>T</mi></math></span></span>, in the rope connecting the blocks change, if at all, as block <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>A</mtext></math></span></span> passes point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>P</mtext></math></span></span>?</p>\n",
